=== 1. Notes and Authoring ===
For notes and authoring I have found the following to be useful:
* [[DeftMode]]: /insert description/.
* [[OrgMode]]: I use [[OrgMode]] for most of my needs in GNU Emacs session; which is primarily writing.
## Toggle the display of unicode characters in an [[OrgMode]] buffer with the command "org-toggle-pretty-entities".

